MOSS-SoundEffect Modly Extension

This repository contains a Modly extension wrapper/integration for MOSS-SoundEffect v2.0.

Upstream model and runtime attribution:

- Model weights: OpenMOSS-Team/MOSS-SoundEffect-v2.0
  https://huggingface.co/OpenMOSS-Team/MOSS-SoundEffect-v2.0

- Runtime/source project: OpenMOSS/MOSS-TTS, moss_soundeffect_v2
  https://github.com/OpenMOSS/MOSS-TTS/tree/main/moss_soundeffect_v2

MOSS-SoundEffect v2.0 and its upstream runtime/model assets are maintained by OpenMOSS/OpenMOSS-Team and are not authored by this extension repository.

This extension repository only provides the Modly process-extension packaging, setup/runtime integration, host compatibility matrix, and workflow artifact handling.

Please review the upstream MOSS-SoundEffect license/model card before redistributing model weights or using generated outputs commercially.
